# Accelerator Integration Working Group

## About

The Accelerator-Integration Working Group is a community group that is exploring a process that accelerators can use to validate changes in the pipeline without blocking the main CI/CD pipeline.  

## Composition

* Open to anyone in the PyTorch community with PyTorch accelerator experience who would like to participate.
* Team is currently collaborating via a public  Slack channel (#tac-accelerator-integration-wg) and a [PR](https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/pull/142114)    
* Meets biweekly - [view calendar](https://zoom-lfx.platform.linuxfoundation.org/meetings/pytorch?view=week).
* Running meeting notes [doc](https://docs.google.com/document/d/10G2fib_76CV4TCf47S-r6R6sg845-ty_ujur_giMNMI/edit?usp=sharing) 
